    "name": "Hemolysis model validation requirement",
    "description": "The hemolysis prediction model shall be validated against physical experimental measurements of hemolysis index obtained from controlled in-vitro pump loop tests. Validation evidence must be traceable to experimental data collected under conditions representative of the VAD operating envelope.",
    "requiredVerificationMethod": "experimental-validation"
  },
