      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Hemolysis model parameter validation via literature survey",
      "description": "A structured review of published hemolysis prediction studies was performed. Seven peer-reviewed sources reporting power-law hemolysis index correlations were identified. The CFD model's empirical constants (C = 3.62e-7, alpha = 2.416, beta = 0.785) were found to fall within the range of values reported in the surveyed literature. This comparison is presented as validation evidence that the model form and parameterisation are consistent with accepted practice.",
